(* Theorem: iterating f x y = MAP (combin$C (FUNPOW f) x) [0 ..< y] *)
(* Proof:
   By induction on y.
   Let g = combin$C (FUNPOW f) x, which is (\j. FUNPOW f j x).
   Base: !x. iterating f x 0 = MAP g [0 ..< 0]
      LHS = iterating f x 0 = []       by iterating_nil
